725843f-a.title: Queens: 127th Street - 18th Avenue
725843f-a.text:
127th Street, east side, at 18th Avenue (vantage point).
lLooking north along the Whitestone branch of the Long Island
Railroad from the College Point station, showing the tracks
passing underneath the 14th Avenue pass.
View 2 is in the same direction from near the l4th Avenue
bridge.
P. L. perr  March 13, 19EE
NO PEPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2

725844f-a.title: Queens: 127th Street - 18th Avenue
725844f-a.text:
127th Street, east side, at 18th Avenue, showing the
College Point station of the Long Island Railroad. View
2 shows the rear of the station facing the tracks, and view
3 is north up the tracks from near 20th Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  March 3, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2,3
